  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "It has all the features, flexibility, art, animation, and power you need to create an environment of your dreams. Choose from a selection of bonus cities and scenarios to rule or ruin as you please. Build schools, libraries, hospitals, zoos, prisons, power plants, and much more... Lay down roads, railways, and highways. Explore the underground layer and build subways and utilities without compromising your aesthetics. Customize different buildings or design your own graphics sets from scratch.\n\nThis is the ultimate classic Maxis city-building and management simulation. If this game were any more realistic, it'd be illegal to turn it off!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ]
